# Wedding Gallery

Drop 8 photos here named exactly:
  1.jpg, 2.jpg, 3.jpg, 4.jpg, 5.jpg, 6.jpg, 7.jpg, 8.jpg

Recommended: 4:5 portrait aspect ratio, at least 1000px wide,
optimized for web (~150-300 KB each).

To add more than 8: edit index.html and copy one of the
.cat-item blocks inside the weddings panel, then bump the
filename (e.g. 9.jpg, 10.jpg).
